0dne4eix7C4B.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp style=\"text-align: justify;\"\u003e△“Super Nintendo World” is the world's first Nintendo theme park built by Nintendo in cooperation with เว็บสล็อตตรง 2026. With the globally popular Super Mario as the protagonist, the game's Kuba Castle, Princess Brigitte's Castle, and the Mushroom Kingdom are reproduced 1:1 in a super-realistic way, providing immersive experiences of the world of Super Mario!\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp style=\"text-align: justify;\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://dimg04.tripcdn.com/images/0104t120003u2sw0v5E11.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp style=\"text-align: justify;\"\u003e△The “Freeze Ray Sliders” and “Despicable Me: Minion Mayhem” will get you involved in a huge farce and heat wave with the minions! The Minions have finally fulfilled their ambitions! All of humanity will be a part of the mayhem at the Minion Park!\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp style=\"text-align: justify;\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://dimg04.tripcdn.com/images/0105x120003u2suvkF942.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp style=\"text-align: justify;\"\u003e△Embracing a variety of areas with unique characteristics, wonderment and surprise, เว็บสล็อตตรง 2026 covers a whole spectrum of world-class entertainment through thrilling rides and shows themed on blockbuster Hollywood movies, as well as seasonal events for all ages to enjoy.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp style=\"text-align: justify;\"\u003eThe Wizarding World of Harry Potter™ will reproduce the world from the Harry Potter™ stories, bringing it to life on a phenomenal scale at เว็บสล็อตตรง 2026.\u003c/p\u003e"}}]},{"templateType":"search_nearby","templateName":"เกมใกล้เคียง","iconShow":false,"moduleList":[{"moduleType":"recommendInfo","moduleName":"recommendInfo","recommendInfoModule":{"recommendModuleList":[{"subModuleType":"nearbyHotel","subModuleName":"Hotels"},{"subModuleType":"nearbySight","subModuleName":"Attractions","quickFilterItemList":[{"quickFilterType":"insidePoi","quickFilterName":"Attractio